1
00:01:24,280 --> 00:01:30,020
[Sunshine of My Life]

2
00:01:30,630 --> 00:01:32,870
[Episode 42]

3
00:01:42,680 --> 00:01:44,180
Xueling.

4
00:01:45,430 --> 00:01:49,340
What's been going on with you lately? Why aren't you picking up my calls?

5
00:01:52,350 --> 00:01:54,620
Is there something going on with you, or...

6
00:01:54,620 --> 00:01:56,440
I think...

7
00:01:57,330 --> 00:01:59,890
we shouldn't see each other anymore.

8
00:02:03,420 --> 00:02:06,610
Did I do something to upset you?

9
00:02:06,610 --> 00:02:08,530
Tell me. I will change.

10
00:02:08,530 --> 00:02:10,850
I know you are sincere towards me.

11
00:02:10,850 --> 00:02:13,520
You treat me really well.

12
00:02:14,830 --> 00:02:17,540
But we aren't suitable for each other.

13
00:02:17,540 --> 00:02:19,970
We can't possibly be together.

14
00:02:19,970 --> 00:02:22,450
Don't waste any more time on me.

15
00:02:22,450 --> 00:02:24,890
I don't want to waste your time.

16
00:02:24,890 --> 00:02:26,420
Why?

17
00:02:26,420 --> 00:02:29,520
We weren't like this before.

18
00:02:29,520 --> 00:02:32,550
During this period of time, didn't you like spending time with me?

19
00:02:32,550 --> 00:02:35,250
You also have feelings for me, right?

20
00:02:36,170 --> 00:02:38,060
Why are you being like this?

21
00:02:38,900 --> 00:02:40,790
Why are you being like this towards me?

22
00:02:40,790 --> 00:02:43,240
Why are you being like this towards yourself?

23
00:02:45,950 --> 00:02:48,340
Because he is still in my heart.

24
00:03:31,030 --> 00:03:34,270
Auntie, I came here to apologize to you.

25
00:03:34,270 --> 00:03:36,560
After I got home, my cousin told me all about

26
00:03:36,560 --> 00:03:39,780
my mom coming here to cause trouble.

27
00:03:40,420 --> 00:03:42,050
Cousin?

28
00:03:42,050 --> 00:03:43,570
I told Lu Zhu.

29
00:03:43,580 --> 00:03:46,080
Who is Lu Zhu?

30
00:03:46,080 --> 00:03:48,520
Mom, we will talk about that later.

31
00:03:48,520 --> 00:03:50,820
Listen to what he has to say first.

32
00:03:57,920 --> 00:04:02,330
Auntie, my mom is sharp-tongued but soft-hearted.

33
00:04:02,330 --> 00:04:04,550
She acts like a little girl when she gets angry.

34
00:04:04,550 --> 00:04:06,530
She has no filter for what she says.

35
00:04:06,530 --> 00:04:11,120
Therefore, Auntie, please just forget about it and do not hold a grudge against her.

36
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:14,180
I am angry.

37
00:04:15,380 --> 00:04:19,720
But from a mother's point of view,

38
00:04:19,720 --> 00:04:21,980
I can understand her.

39
00:04:21,990 --> 00:04:24,890
Because she is concerned about her son.

40
00:04:24,890 --> 00:04:29,420
From my point of view, as long as you are serious about Mo Fei,

41
00:04:29,420 --> 00:04:32,180
I have no issues.

42
00:04:32,180 --> 00:04:33,950
However,

43
00:04:34,660 --> 00:04:37,650
if you two end up together,

44
00:04:37,650 --> 00:04:40,300
both families' approval

45
00:04:40,300 --> 00:04:43,160
is the key to your happiness.

46
00:04:43,170 --> 00:04:45,820
Therefore, about your mother,

47
00:04:46,630 --> 00:04:49,450
you must resolve that yourself.

48
00:04:51,050 --> 00:04:53,690
Auntie, in regards to that, you do not need to worry at all.

49
00:04:53,690 --> 00:04:55,890
It's my mom, so I will deal with her.

50
00:04:55,890 --> 00:04:59,370
Even if I can't get through to her, my mom has always disapproved of my relationships.

51
00:04:59,370 --> 00:05:02,840
I can make my own decisions when it comes to my relationships.

52
00:05:07,230 --> 00:05:09,850
Ever since the day Mo Fei and I got together,

53
00:05:11,890 --> 00:05:14,570
I wanted to eventually get married.

54
00:05:21,100 --> 00:05:23,230
Since you have said that,

55
00:05:25,500 --> 00:05:27,770
I am relieved.

56
00:05:27,770 --> 00:05:30,390
But you should also think carefully

57
00:05:30,390 --> 00:05:33,920
about how you will tell your mother about this.

58
00:05:33,930 --> 00:05:35,730
I understand.

59
00:05:39,980 --> 00:05:41,440
I am sorry.

60
00:05:48,790 --> 00:05:51,630
Xueling said she won't get married anymore. She is angry now.

61
00:05:51,630 --> 00:05:53,450
Go comfort her.

62
00:05:57,130 --> 00:06:00,760
What's wrong, Empress Dowager? Are you in a bad mood?

63
00:06:02,100 --> 00:06:04,040
How could I dare be in a bad mood?

64
00:06:04,040 --> 00:06:07,950
Every day, I must act accordingly to your will. I dare not. I am in a great mood.

65
00:06:07,950 --> 00:06:12,420
Forget that. Whose will have you ever acted according to?

66
00:06:12,420 --> 00:06:14,300
Yours.

67
00:06:14,300 --> 00:06:16,440
How could I dare to?

68
00:06:18,420 --> 00:06:21,530
I'm not angry at Xueling.

69
00:06:21,530 --> 00:06:23,620
I'm just thinking, you are not young anymore,

70
00:06:23,630 --> 00:06:25,180
so why are you still so immature?

71
00:06:25,180 --> 00:06:26,850
Why are you so slow-minded?

72
00:06:26,850 --> 00:06:28,860
Do you think your son is slow-minded?

73
00:06:28,860 --> 00:06:30,860
He wasn't before, but he is now.

74
00:06:30,860 --> 00:06:32,650
Now that you've been met with love, not only you are slow-minded,

75
00:06:32,650 --> 00:06:34,160
you are a little dummy.

76
00:06:34,160 --> 00:06:37,510
Listen, Mom. Let me talk to you about the Fang Weiguo situation.

77
00:06:37,510 --> 00:06:41,610
Since the beginning of this matter, I have thought of a resolution.

78
00:06:41,610 --> 00:06:44,080
- What resolution?
- I can't say right now.

79
00:06:44,080 --> 00:06:47,180
- You are just trying to pacify me.
- I am not!

80
00:06:47,180 --> 00:06:51,610
If I cannot resolve this matter, no matter what you say in the future,

81
00:06:51,610 --> 00:06:53,240
I will listen to you.

82
00:06:53,250 --> 00:06:58,270
Keep delaying it. Delay it until Mingyuan isn't ours anymore and then you will finally be happy.

83
00:06:58,270 --> 00:07:00,210
Trust me, Mom.

84
00:07:01,200 --> 00:07:04,890
You've got blinded by that Mo Fei. You can't see anything clearly anymore.

85
00:07:05,930 --> 00:07:07,660
You should know she is very formidable.

86
00:07:07,660 --> 00:07:09,640
Her little mouth won't stop talking.

87
00:07:09,640 --> 00:07:13,530
There is logic, reasoning, and parallelism in her words. So annoying.

88
00:07:13,530 --> 00:07:15,890
Does she have that side to her?

89
00:07:15,890 --> 00:07:18,440
Of course, she wouldn't show this side of hers to you.

90
00:07:18,440 --> 00:07:19,870
But I saw it.

91
00:07:19,870 --> 00:07:21,570
She's a small person doing great mischief.

92
00:07:21,570 --> 00:07:25,960
She's so young and already two-faced. What will she be like in the future?

93
00:07:25,960 --> 00:07:30,620
Look at how outstanding of a girl Mo Fei is. I have never seen this side of her.

94
00:07:30,620 --> 00:07:32,350
W-What does this prove?

95
00:07:32,350 --> 00:07:34,650
That she is intelligent and responsible.

96
00:07:34,650 --> 00:07:37,630
Did you know that, after meeting you a few times now, she has never told me about it?

97
00:07:37,630 --> 00:07:40,880
Mom, what you and her need most

98
00:07:40,880 --> 00:07:46,290
is to communicate and interact more. I will bring her home to chat with you and dad when I have time. Okay?

99
00:07:46,290 --> 00:07:48,200
Thank you, Young Master.

100
00:07:48,200 --> 00:07:51,620
Please don't bring her here. I don't want to get to know her, I don't want to see her.

101
00:07:51,620 --> 00:07:53,430
Move. I want to rest now.

102
00:07:53,440 --> 00:07:55,570
Mom, Mo Fei is especially great at making clothes.

103
00:07:55,570 --> 00:07:57,480
I will have her make a few outfits for you, all right?

104
00:07:57,480 --> 00:08:01,320
Am I so destitute now that I have to ask her to make my clothes?

105
00:08:01,320 --> 00:08:03,890
I still have money for that.

106
00:08:05,510 --> 00:08:07,710
She also knows how to make jewelry.

107
00:08:08,930 --> 00:08:10,880
I don't believe that.

108
00:08:11,750 --> 00:08:14,780
Let me tell you! Don't even think about marrying her.

109
00:08:16,680 --> 00:08:18,420
I must marry her.

110
00:08:25,300 --> 00:08:27,870
"Little mouth won't stop talking?"

111
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:31,350
She depicts her quite vividly.

112
00:08:33,140 --> 00:08:34,670
Mom.

113
00:08:36,630 --> 00:08:38,310
Thank you.

114
00:08:39,090 --> 00:08:41,000
For what?

115
00:08:42,150 --> 00:08:46,570
Thank you for not making it difficult for Mingxuan.

116
00:08:48,250 --> 00:08:50,910
Did you think I am that kind of person?

117
00:08:55,850 --> 00:08:58,190
I feel so happy.

118
00:09:00,840 --> 00:09:05,830
Since my daughter is happy, I, as your mother, am happy too.

119
00:09:10,090 --> 00:09:12,220
However, my daughter,

120
00:09:12,220 --> 00:09:16,300
this is only your first step on this long journey of love.

121
00:09:16,300 --> 00:09:20,840
There will be many obstacles and hardships you will have to put up with in the future.

122
00:09:20,840 --> 00:09:24,210
You will have to face them by yourself.

123
00:09:26,220 --> 00:09:31,000
Because... in this world,

124
00:09:32,290 --> 00:09:35,520
even the most unwavering love

125
00:09:36,230 --> 00:09:39,670
may become weaker

126
00:09:40,500 --> 00:09:42,820
become bad,

127
00:09:42,820 --> 00:09:46,710
or disappear with the passage of time.

128
00:09:52,540 --> 00:09:54,440
Mom,

129
00:09:54,440 --> 00:09:56,860
you must trust your daughter.

130
00:09:58,130 --> 00:10:00,340
I definitely will

131
00:10:01,270 --> 00:10:03,250
live very happily.

132
00:10:06,840 --> 00:10:08,590
I believe that.

133
00:10:22,930 --> 00:10:25,980
When did you become so romantic?

134
00:10:26,770 --> 00:10:30,640
- It's for you.
- I know. Who else would you gift it to?

135
00:10:30,640 --> 00:10:33,390
Do you remember what you promised me?

136
00:10:33,390 --> 00:10:36,350
- What did I promise you?
- Give me your phone.

137
00:10:36,350 --> 00:10:38,840
