148
00:11:20,210 --> 00:11:24,440
I think you and Mo Fei can make a list to go do.

149
00:11:29,490 --> 00:11:31,610
Have you done all of these before?

150
00:11:32,600 --> 00:11:36,550
Of course. When I date, they are all normal relationships.

151
00:11:37,330 --> 00:11:39,370
