165
00:12:22,980 --> 00:12:26,330
All right, get to work. I must learn these well.

166
00:12:26,330 --> 00:12:30,310
- How about I teach you?
- You want to teach me?
- I was joking.

167
00:12:30,310 --> 00:12:32,720
